@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hcpgwc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs((0.93 + v1))
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.exp((v0 + 0.87 / tmp + 0.19)))
    tmp = ((v1 + v0) * v0)
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v0 + 0.08)) - wp.sin(v0))
    v1 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
